comment: /**  * Gets the comparator that sorts a..z  */
code: /**  * Gets the comparator that sorts a..z  */ public static OrderedComparator get() {     return INSTANCE. }

comment: /**  * Gets the comparator that sorts z..a (reverse)  */
code: /**  * Gets the comparator that sorts z..a (reverse)  */ public static OrderedComparator getReverse() {     return INSTANCE_REVERSE. }

public int compare(Object o1, Object o2) {     Integer num1 = 0.     Integer num2 = 0.     if (o1 instanceof Ordered) {         num1 = ((Ordered) o1).getOrder().     }     if (o2 instanceof Ordered) {         num2 = ((Ordered) o2).getOrder().     }     int answer = num1.compareTo(num2).     return reverse ? -1 * answer : answer. }
